    "All data, code and ratings can be found at https://github.com/jekunz/ llm-expl-properties.",
    "We use Alpaca (Taori et al., 2023), a dataset automatically generated using the self-instruct pipeline (Wang et al., 2022), in the version with GPT-4 annotations (Peng et al., 2023).",
